The consideration of human oversight and software resources in the development of AI systems is relevant to the sub-category of cs.HC (human-computer interaction). Finally, the paper's focus on the life cycle of AI systems and the need to set milestones for future progress is relevant to the sub-category of cs.SE (software engineering).
